# ClassQuest Module 4 Lesson 1 Rules

## Scope

You are developing:

```text
src/modules/module-4-ai-info-detective/lessons/lesson-1
```

This lesson is local-first frontend only.

## Must Do

- Keep all lesson-1 business components inside module-4.
- Use Module4Lesson1State.
- Implement 5 steps:
  - Step1MissionBrief
  - Step2SampleObservation
  - Step3CardAnatomy
  - Step4QuizFlowDemo
  - Step5TaskChecklist
- Implement Guard.
- Keep routes under `/module/4/lesson/1`.
- Update lesson README and FILE-STRUCTURE after changes.

## Must Not Do

- Do not call backend APIs.
- Do not introduce SQLite.
- Do not implement teacher review.
- Do not create submission_pack_id or edit_token.
- Do not import module-3 business types.
- Do not move module-4 business components into shared.
- Do not use WebSocket.
- Do not expose technical terms like JSON/schema/repository to students.

## UI Rule

Student-facing text should use classroom language:

- 题目卡
- 来源记录
- 核验入口
- 任务清单
- 继续学习包
- 阶段快照

Avoid:

- JSON
- schema
- repository
- API
- token
- SQLite

## Completion Rule

Step 5 completion must set:

```ts
lesson1.completed = true
```

If Lesson 2 is not implemented, return to Module 4 home with a completion message.
